description: Investment Alert in South Boston's most sought after City Point neighborhood!  This multi-family offers over 4,000 square feet of living space with 9 existing bedrooms and 6 bathrooms spanning over 4 floors!  Inside, you'll find condo quality finishes such as renovated kitchens and bathrooms, beautiful hardwood and tile floors, along with generous living and bedroom spaces. Enjoy outdoor living on the deck or backyard for your personal enjoyment. Abundant on-street parking adds ease to city living.  These apartments rent in a heartbeat each year with no vacancy.  Easy potential to increase rent by adding additional bedrooms.
